<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
Due to the general cyclonic pattern over the British Isles and Scandinavia, we could see in these regions the negative anomalies in radiation and positive anomalies in cloud cover which was extra remarkable after a very sunny spring and first part of the summer.
